Private Events
Let Tequila Daisy host your next event!
Contact us for your next event!
Looking to elevate your next private event? Tequila Daisy is the place! Nestled in the heart of downtown St. Petersburg, our vibrant tequila bar is the perfect backdrop for birthdays, bridal showers, bachelor parties, corporate events and more.
The space at Tequila Daisy holds up to 190 guests and includes two bars (one large, one small), a DJ booth, moveable tables that can be arranged in various configurations, a dance floor and photo-worthy murals and decor for that perfect Instagram shot!
